private theorem sub_sub_cancel (m n : ℕ) (h : m ≤ n) : n - (n - m) = m :=
  calc
    n - (n - m) = n - m + m - (n - m) := by rw [nat.sub_add_cancel] <;> assumption
    _ = m := nat.add_sub_cancel_left _ _
    
#align sub_sub_cancel sub_sub_cancel
